      "content": "Hey, I'm a corporate wellness coach working with some execs at a high-end consulting firm. They're preparing for some really high-stakes boardroom presentations and want to make sure their physical presentation matches their level of authority. Can you give me some general tips on grooming, hair, and overall appearance that help project a sense of professionalism and command in a corporate setting?",
