    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a solid start. One thing my clients have brought up is how to handle hair. Specifically, they're wondering about what qualifies as \"neat\" or \"professional\" when it comes to different hair textures or styles. For example, if someone has very natural, textured hair or wears it in certain culturally specific ways, how should they approach it to make sure they still look authoritative and not \"distracting\" in a boardroom?",
